quran[15{c,v,t}:
23,75,agar hum inn par reham karen aur woh takleef jis mein aaj kal yeh mubtala hain door kar den to yeh apni sar kashi mein bilkul hi behak jayen ge
23,76,"inn ka haal to yeh hai ke hum ne inhen takleef mein mubtala kya, phir bhi yeh apne rab ke agay nah jhuke aur nah aajzi ikhtiyar karte hain"
23,77,Albata jab nobat yahan taq poanch jaye gi ke hum inn par sakht azaab ka darwaaza khol den ge to yakayak tum dekho ge ke is haalat mein yeh har kher se mayoos hain
23,78,woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumhe sُnne aur dekhnay ki quwaten den aur sochnay ko dil diye magar tum log kam hi shukar guzaar hotay ho
23,79,"wohi hai jis ne tumhe zameen mein phelaya, aur isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
23,80,wohi zindagi bakhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai gardish Lail o nehar isi ke qabza qudrat mein hai kya tumhari samajh mein yeh baat nahi aati ?
23,81,magar yeh log wohi kuch kehte hain jo un ke paish ro keh chuke hain
23,82,"yeh kehte hain"" kya jab hum mar kar matti ho jayen ge aur hadion ka panjar ban kar reh jayen ge to hum ko phir zindah kar ke uthaya jaye ga ?"
23,83,"hum ne bhi yeh waday bohat sunay hain aur hum se pehlay hamaray baap dada bhi suntay rahay hain yeh mehez afsanaha-ay Parinah hain """
23,84,"un se kaho, batao agar tum jantay ho, ke yeh zameen aur is ki saari abadi kis ki hai ?"
23,85,"yeh zaroor kahin ge Allah ki kaho, phir tum hosh mein kyun nahi atay ?"
23,86,"un se pucho, saton asmano aur arsh azeem ka maalik kon hai ?"
23,87,"yeh zaroor kahin ge Allah kaho, phir tum drtay kyun nahi ?"
23,88,"inn se kaho, batao agar tum jantay ho ke har cheez par Iqtidaar kis ka hai? aur kon hai woh jo panah deta hai aur is ke muqablay mein koi panah nahi day sakta ?"
23,89,"yeh zaroor kahin ge ke yeh baat to Allah hi ke liye hai kaho, phir kahan se tum ko dhoka lagta hai ?"
